descriptionHtml:
*I am still learning about modding Skyrim.  I am trying to add lights inside my Shanty, but they don\'t seem to light the interior.  Part of the ceiling seems to get lit, but not the walls or floor, or anything else.  Help would be appreciated.

A simple Shanty in Dawnstar. It is located on the coast North of the Museum of the Mythic Dawn.

I did not decorate the interior on purpose.  I personally use other MODs that allow me to move objects and decorate as I desire.  I wanted a good starter home that made since for an immigrant to Skyrim.

This Shanty does not load an interior cell.  I built it in the Dawnstar exterior cell.  I like the idea of being able to look out the windows and see the world.  

I know this is far from a perfect home.  This was very much a test.  I will improve upon it further and update it as I learn more about making these kinds of MODs. 

I use Iceburg\'s Placeable Statics MOD to decorate this shanty. http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/users/1398716/?
author: Nyx Kordel
